Note: in Desktop mode, press "2" to equip the Development Tool.
1. Open Dashboard and select "Inventory"
2. "Resonite Essentials"
3. "Tools"
4. Double-click the Development Tool to spawn a tool
5. Select the tool, select "Equip Development Tool"
6. Select your tool shelf to store the tool
Note: in Desktop mode, press "4" to equip the Material Tool
7. Double-click the Material Tool to spawn a tool
8. Select the tool, select "Equip Material Tool"
9. Click on the Development Tool on your tool shelf to swap tools
